Introduction
Welcome to SpendWise! We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information when you use our app. By using SpendWise, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

Information Collection and Use
Data Collection: SpendWise does not collect, store, or share any personal data from its users. We do not collect any information that can be used to identify you personally.

Permissions: The only permission we request is for notifications. This is solely to send you reminders to track your expenses. SpendWise does not collect or store any data related to your notifications.

Notification Permissions
SpendWise requests permission to send notifications for the following purposes:

To remind you to track your expenses.
You can manage your notification preferences in your device settings at any time.

Security
We are committed to ensuring that your information is secure. Since we do not collect any data, there are no security risks related to data breaches or unauthorized access to your personal information.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. Changes are effective as soon as they are posted.

Contact Us
